## Conventions

- Type hints required cho function signature (mypy strict)
- Black + Ruff format/lint qua hook
- Migration: tạo manual (`makemigrations -n <descriptive_name>`), không auto-merge
- Test placement: `<app>/tests/` với pytest-style

